                                        to create crud functionalities on the client side. The GET POST methods are there in the web api project, just need to allow user to perform those 
                                        functionalities on the client side. Also, need to create a few admins in the database, so they can create programs and courses, and the user can select
                                        from available list. 
                                    </p>
                                   
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="col-md-2 hidden-sm col-xs-12">
                            <div class="footer-content">
                                <div class="footer-head">
                                    <h4>Programs</h4>
                                    <ul class="footer-list">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.sheridancollege.ca/programs">Programs offered at Sheridan</a></li>
                                        
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                       
                        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12">
                            <div class="footer-content">
                                <div class="footer-head">
                                    <h4>Apply Now</h4>
                                    <ul class="footer-list">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.sheridancollege.ca/admissions/how-to-apply">How To Apply</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        
                        <div class="col-md-2 col-sm-3 col-xs-12">
                            <div class="footer-content last-content">
                                <div class="footer-head">
                                    <h4>FAQ</h4>
                                    <ul class="footer-list">
                                        <li><a href="https://www.sheridancollege.ca/programs">Frequently Asked Question</a></li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>

            </div>

            <!-- Start Footer Bottom Area -->
            <div class="footer-area-bottom">
                <div class="container">
                    <div class="row">
